On our group server we have netCDF installation compiled ... 

In the past we have found that attempting to install netCDF in parallel has resulted in some strange behaviour in other applications (e.g. GRASS...). To get around this issue, I made a local netCDF installation with parallel mode enabled. The basic guide I followed is the (Quick Instructions for Installing NetCDF on Unix)[https://www.unidata.ucar.edu/software/netcdf/netcdf-4/newdocs/netcdf-install/Quick-Instructions-for-Installing-NetCDF-on-Unix.html].

